{"lemma":"باغ","slug":"باغ","root":"ب.غ.#","root_slug":"ب-غ-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-غ-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"باغ","root":"بغي","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2969"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%BA"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2969","headword_ar":"بَاغٍ","root":"bgY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seeking; seeking for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after; seeking, desiring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavouring, to find, and take,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"get:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bugaApN","text_ar":"بُغَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bugoyaAnN","text_ar":"بُغْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bug~aA='N","text_ar":"بُغَّا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA: [there mentioned as a pl., but not said to be of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAgK","text_ar":"بَاغٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", nor explained.])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAgK wahaAdK","text_ar":"بَاغٍ وَهَادٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seeker"},{"kind":"text","text":"of [stray] camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and a guide"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the way, mentioned in a trad. respecting the Hijreh (as said by A booBekr to a man who asked him “ Who are ye? ”), alludes to the seeking of religion and the guiding from error. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"far~iquwA lih`*ihi AlA_ibili","text_ar":"فَرِّقُوا لِهٰذِهِ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bugoyaAnFA yuDib~uwna lahaA","text_ar":"بُغْيَانًا يُضِبُّونَ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disperse ye, for these camels, seekers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to scatter themselves in search thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Acting wrongfully, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.,] towards others: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bugaApN","text_ar":"بُغَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb. [See 1.])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayora baAgK","text_ar":"غَيْرَ بَاغٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur ii. 168, [&c.,] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Not being a revolter from the Muslims,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel,) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against the Imám:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not desiring to eat for the sake of enjoyment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not seeking to exceed the limit of his want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not seeking what he should not seek."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiy^apN baAgiyahN","text_ar":"فِيَةٌ بَاغِيَهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company of men revolting from the just Imám."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoqapN","text_ar":"فِرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAgiyapN","text_ar":"بَاغِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party occupying itself with corrupt, wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unjust, conduct."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that does not impregnate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"get with young."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, K.) ―         -b4-  A horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is proud,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"self-conceited, with exceeding briskness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liveliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Ham p. 210:) [but] Kh disallows its being thus used. (S.)       -A2-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bugoyaAnN","text_ar":"بُغْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What the sportsman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hunter, seeks, of game,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"objects of the chase."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabogFY","text_ar":"مَبْغًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place where a thing is sought:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":233},{"kind":"text","text":"hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, in which a thing is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"should be, sought"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: this is meant in the saying, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bagayotu AlmaAla mino mabogaAtihi","text_ar":"بَغَيْتُ المَالَ مِنْ مَبْغَاتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sought wealth by the way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, whereby it should be sought"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA^otFY","text_ar":"مَاْتًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is meant in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotu AlA^amora","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُ الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino maA^otaAtihi","text_ar":"مِنْ مَاْتَاتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Jel","TA","Az"]}]}}